1.5
log
@d@@ has asked me to put in an explicit "Public domain" on header files for code
he's written here.  The code itself is clearly licensed already.
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: conf.h,v 1.4 2002/02/16 21:27:10 millert Exp $	*/
